<h3>Project description</h3>

<p>Debian-Installer is a major project which was initiated shortly
after the woody release. As the name implies, it will be the installer
for sarge.  It bears no resemblance to the previous boot-floppies
installer. It uses a plug-in architecture to support various installer
modules. Debconf was used as the primary UI, and a rewrite of debconf
in C was undertaken in support of debian-installer.</p>

